   <concept id="FAR_22_1310" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">22.1310</ph> Solicitation provision
and contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1442e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1464e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol id="d1442e23" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1464e15">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> Insert the clause at <xref href="52.222-35.dita#FAR_52_222_35"
                              base="i1056230"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.222-35</xref>, Equal Opportunity for Veterans, in solicitations and contracts if the expected value is <ph rev="FAC 2025-06 October 1, 2025" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2024-001?>$200,000<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 22.1310 in paragraph (a)(1) by removing “$150,000” and adding “$200,000” in its place.?></ph> or more, except when-</p>
                     <ol id="d1442e36" class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d1464e24">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph> Work is performed
outside the United States by employees recruited outside the United
States; or</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d1464e29">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph> The Director,
Office of Federal Contract Compliance Programs of the U.S. Department
of Labor, has waived, in accordance with <xref href="22.1305.dita#FAR_22_1305"
                                    base="i1096080"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">22.1305</xref>(a), or the head
of the agency has waived, in accordance with <xref href="22.1305.dita#FAR_22_1305"
                                    base="i1096080"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">22.1305</xref>(b), all of the terms
of the clause.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1464e40">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> If the
Director, Office of Federal Contract Compliance Programs of the
U.S. Department of Labor, or the head of the agency waives one or
more (but not all) of the terms of the clause, use the basic clause
with its Alternate I.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1464e45">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Insert
the clause at <xref href="52.222-37.dita#FAR_52_222_37"
                        base="i1056265"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-37</xref>,
Employment Reports on Veterans, in solicitations and contracts containing
the clause at <xref href="52.222-35.dita#FAR_52_222_35"
                        base="i1056230"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-35</xref>,
Equal Opportunity for Veterans.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1464e56">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> Insert
the provision at <xref href="52.222-38.dita#FAR_52_222_38"
                        base="i1056289"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.222-38</xref>,
Compliance with Veterans’ Employment Reporting Requirements, in
solicitations when it is anticipated the contract award will exceed
the simplified acquisition threshold and the contract is not for
acquisition of commercial
products or commercial services.
               </p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
